commit.message: Remove unused/superseded variable definition in tests
Avoid an infinite loop if we fail to parse any tokens
Support '=' and '==' on the end of terminal tokens (for Negotiate)
Lowercase expected scheme names in tests to match new casefolding.
Use explicit super() call for backwards compatibility
Make group_* functions internal by addition of initial '_'.
casefold/lower keys in challenges, as RFC 7235 says auth scheme names are case-insensitive
Change package name from using underscore to hyphen
